lines.text: Don't go in there, devil himself lives in there. You'll never come out alive.
Don't listen to him Stella, I make deliveries here, it's fine food.
Are you sure? It looks a little evil in there.
Your princess, if the bitch really exists, is welcome to try and stop me!
Holy shit! You assholes! What's going on here?
Excuse me, asshole! I'm here about the fucking job!
